    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert business proposal writer specializing in B2B consulting and automation services.\n\nGenerate a comprehensive, professional proposal based on the following client requirements. You MUST return your response as a valid JSON object ONLY, with no additional text before or after.\n\nCLIENT CONTEXT:\n{{ $json.ai_context }}\n\nREQUIRED JSON STRUCTURE:\n{\n  \"executive_summary\": \"2-3 paragraph overview highlighting the opportunity, proposed approach, and expected outcomes\",\n  \"problem_statement\": \"Detailed understanding of the client's challenge, pain points, and business context (3-4 paragraphs)\",\n  \"proposed_solution\": \"Comprehensive solution approach, methodology, and how it addresses the problem (4-5 paragraphs)\",\n  \"scope_of_work\": [\n    \"Specific work item 1 with details\",\n    \"Specific work item 2 with details\",\n    \"Specific work item 3 with details\",\n    \"... (minimum 5 items)\"\n  ],\n  \"deliverables\": [\n    \"Concrete deliverable 1 with description\",\n    \"Concrete deliverable 2 with description\",\n    \"... (minimum 4 deliverables)\"\n  ],\n  \"timeline\": \"Structured timeline with phases and milestones (can be text or array)\",\n  \"assumptions\": [\n    \"Key assumption 1\",\n    \"Key assumption 2\",\n    \"... (minimum 3 assumptions)\"\n  ],\n  \"out_of_scope\": [\n    \"Explicitly excluded item 1\",\n    \"Explicitly excluded item 2\",\n    \"... (minimum 3 items)\"\n  ],\n  \"next_steps\": \"Clear call-to-action paragraph with specific next steps for the client\"\n}\n\nWRITING GUIDELINES:\n- Use professional, consultative tone\n- Be specific but avoid overpromising\n- Use \"we will\" and \"our team\" language\n- Include measurable outcomes where possible\n- Keep timeline realistic based on complexity\n- Be clear about what IS and ISN'T included\n- Make assumptions explicit to manage expectations\n- End with clear, actionable next steps\n\nReturn ONLY the JSON object, nothing else.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [
        976,
        -16
      ],
      "id": "eba73bea-84ee-4d3e-bd3b-ea21a67d0e50",
      "name": "AI Agent (Generate Proposal)"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const items = $input.all();\nlet proposalData;\n\ntry {\n  // Get AI response\n  const aiResponse = items[0].json.output || items[0].json.text || items[0].json;\n  \n  // Parse JSON if it's a string\n  if (typeof aiResponse === 'string') {\n    // Remove markdown code blocks if present\n    const cleaned = aiResponse.replace(/```json\\n?/g, '').replace(/```\\n?/g, '').trim();\n    proposalData = JSON.parse(cleaned);\n  } else {\n    proposalData = aiResponse;\n  }\n  \n  // Get original data from earlier node\n  const originalData = items[0].json;\n  \n  // Validate required fields\n  const requiredFields = ['executive_summary', 'problem_statement', 'proposed_solution', \n                          'scope_of_work', 'deliverables', 'timeline', \n                          'assumptions', 'out_of_scope', 'next_steps'];\n  \n  const missingFields = requiredFields.filter(field => !proposalData[field]);\n  \n  if (missingFields.length > 0) {\n    throw new Error(`Missing required fields: ${missingFields.join(', ')}`);\n  }\n  \n  return [{\n    json: {\n      ...originalData,\n      proposal: proposalData,\n      status: \"success\",\n      parse_error: null\n    }\n  }];\n  \n} catch (error) {\n  // Return error state\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      ...items[0].json,\n      proposal: null,\n      status: \"parse_error\",\n      parse_error: error.message\n    }\n  }];\n}"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
